<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-4bw+/aepP/YC94hEpVNVgiZdgIC5+VKNBQNGCHeKRQN+PtmoHDEXuppvnDJzQIu9" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-HwwvtgBNo3bZJJLYd8oVXjrBZt8cqVSpeBNS5n7C8IVInixGAoxmnlMuBnhbgrkm" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.7.2/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="Css/Homepage.css">
    <title>Secret Coffee</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('./header.ejs');%>


      <div id="content-container">

        <!-- Carousell-->
      <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
          <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
          <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
          <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="carousel-inner text-center">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="Gallery/wallpaper1.jpg" alt="First slide" height="500px">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-flex h-100 align-items-center justify-content-center" style="flex-direction: column;">
              <h1>MORE THAN JUST COFFEE</h1>
              <h2 >Our beans come from 3 primary locations around the world</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img  class="d-block w-100" src="Gallery/wallpaper2.jpg" alt="Second slide" height="500px">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-flex h-100 align-items-center justify-content-center" style="flex-direction: column;">
              <h3>Experience our aromatic<br> coffee blends</h3>
              <p> Brewed to perfection</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img  class="d-block w-100" src="Gallery/wallpaper3.jpg" alt="Third slide" height="500px">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-flex h-100 align-items-center justify-content-center" style="flex-direction: column;"> 
              <h3>Open your morning ritual<br> with our coffee collection</h3>
              <p>We have the perfect blend to kickstart your day</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
      </div>

       <!-- End OfCarousell-->

       <div class="container marketing">

        <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <img class="bd-placeholder-img rounded-circle" width="140" height="140" src="/Gallery/brazil_flag.png" aria-label="Placeholder: 140x140"><title>Placeholder</title><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#777"/></img>
            <h2>Brazil</h2>
            <p>Indulge in the rich, smooth flavors of Brazilian coffee beans. With their mild acidity and notes of chocolate and caramel, Brazilian coffee beans are the perfect choice for those who appreciate a classic, full-bodied brew.
               Explore our selection of Brazilian coffee and experience the essence of Brazil in every cup</p>
            <!-- <p><a class="btn btn-light" href="allproudcts/filters/country1" >Shop From Brazil now! &raquo;</a></p> -->
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <img class="bd-placeholder-img rounded-circle" width="140" height="140" src="/Gallery/ethiopia_flag.png" aria-label="Placeholder: 140x140"><title>Placeholder</title><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#777"/></img>    
            <h2>Ethiopia</h2>
            <p>Take a sensory journey with our Ethiopian coffee beans. From the birthplace of coffee, these beans promise an exotic adventure. Whether you prefer the fruity notes of Yirgacheffe or the spicy tones of Sidamo, our Ethiopian coffee selection brings the rich coffee culture of Ethiopia to your cup.</p>
            <!-- <p><a class="btn btn-light" href="allproudcts/filters/country3">Shop From Ethiopia now! &raquo;</a></p> -->
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <img class="bd-placeholder-img rounded-circle" width="140" height="140" src="/Gallery/colombia_flag.png" aria-label="Placeholder: 140x140"><title>Placeholder</title><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#777"/></img>    
            <h2>Colombia</h2>
            <p>Experience the excellence of Colombian coffee. Our Colombian coffee beans offer a harmonious blend of citrusy brightness, medium body, and delightful hints of caramel, and nuts.
               By choosing our Colombian coffee you also support sustainable and ethical coffee farming practices in Colombia.</p>
            <!-- <p><a class="btn btn-light" href="allproudcts/filters/country2">Shop From Colombia now! &raquo;</a></p> -->
          </div>>
        </div>
    
          
        <!-- FEATURETTES -->
    
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
    
        <div class="row featurette">
          <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">BE your own barista. <span class="text-muted"> Every day, any time.</span></h2>
            <p class="lead"> Becoming your own barista is a journey of empowerment, allowing you to craft your coffee just the way you like it.
               It's about seizing control over your daily caffeine fix, tailoring it to your unique preferences.
                With the right beans, brewing methods, and a dash of creativity, you become the curator of your coffee experience, from creamy lattes to bold, black cups of morning motivation.
                So, embrace the art of coffee-making, and savor the satisfaction of crafting your beloved brew independently, one delightful cup at a time.

            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5">
            <img class="bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" width="500" height="200" src="/Gallery/barista.png" aria-label="Placeholder: 500x500" focusable="false"><title>Placeholder</title><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#eee"/></img>    
          </div>
        </div>
    
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
    
        <div class="row featurette">
          <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">How can you determine which coffee suits your taste preferences perfectly? <span class="text-muted"></span></h2>
            <p class="lead">Choosing the perfect coffee to suit your unique tastes is a delightful journey of exploration. It's a quest that allows you to craft your daily ritual into a personalized experience.
              From the bold and robust flavors of a dark roast to the bright, fruity notes of a light roast, there's a coffee waiting to captivate your senses. 
              So, embrace the adventure and let your taste buds guide you in discovering the coffee that truly resonates with your palate, making each cup a moment to savor and enjoy.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
            <img class="bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" width="500" height="200" src="/Gallery/wallpaper4.jpg" aria-label="Placeholder: 500x500" focusable="false"><title>Placeholder</title><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#eee"/></img>
    
          </div>
        </div>
    
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
    
        <div class="row featurette">
          <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">And lastly, check out how to be A MASTER. <span class="text-muted"></span></h2>
            <p class="lead">Master the art of coffee-making with our video guide. <br><h4>Click to watch!</h4></p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5">
            <div class="video-container">
              <iframe width="650" height="400" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gbcirvLA23A?si=jFlBreejrI4Cxz-q" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
    
        <!-- /END THE FEATURETTES -->
      </div><!-- /.container -->


      </div>


      <%- include('./footer.ejs');%>


    <!-- Optional JavaScript -->
    <!-- jQuery first, then Popper.js, then Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.4/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <!-- <script src="Homepage.js"></script> -->
  </body>
</html>
